---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Notes:
    - electrolux.postman_collection.json is postman collection to create fake notification and add it into the queue which will send connection status in every 60 sec.
    - FakeStatusGeneratorController is used to create fake connection status for appliances 
    - FakeNotificationService will queued the fake connections of the appliances and send status in every 60 sec to the  rest endpoint http://localhost:8080/appliances/connection/update to update status.
    - AppliancesController controller has end point /appliances/connection/status , whihc can show connection status of appliances along with customer details. 
